===Noun===
'''claves'''

# {{musici}} {{plural of|[[clave]]}} Claves are a [[percussion]] instrument, consisting of two [[stick]]s or [[block]]s, in which one is [[struck]] against the other in order to produce a sound.

====Usage notes====
One generally speaks of playing "the claves"; the singular form is seldom used.

